we will be meeting at Railroad Square (middle of Main Street) at 11:00-11:30 ish to distribute material and job assignments. Bring your slim jims and Ron Paul Gear. Call Steven if you need more info. 802 779-4447

We'll hand out Ron Paul Material to the over 10,000 people in attendance at the Pumpkin fest. Starting at 10 am and going until sundown, volunteers will hand out material to those in the crowd. Work a half hour, hour or all day if you wish. Cheshire County Coordinater John Lewicke will be at Railroad Square between noon & 4 pm with literature, signs, etc. for campaigners. He is & will be coordinating for people to be passing out lit & collecting names. If interested or attending Pumpkin Fest please contact him at: JohnL@RonPaul.2012.com
item.name: Literature drop at the Keene Pumpkin Fest
